text: <!channel> good morning! Another weird morning for me, and I'm WFH today, so let's do another virtual standup.
working with josh on cleaning design for cms - working with phill on wallpaper images
Cool. Did you see my email that they want all 88?
yep
Cool, hopefully that won't take too terribly long
download the 88 and size them for kat
let us know about the credits and will start asap
I loaded enough for 16
But you'll need more
Account info is in the email, and anyone with a company cc can do it
ok - i added stephanie to the email.

<@U02688JHZ> I finished up the basics of the data model in the datastore, there's CRUD endpoints in place for all of: device, newsitem, about, and scheduled pushes. I merged all the backend server stuff in with joshua's CMS project and got it deployed and  up and running on app engine:  <http://tidy-federation-859.appspot.com/messages>
today i'm going to work on scheduled tasks to publish pending news items and send scheduled pushes, and work with joshua and kat to give them what they need
oh also something in the datastore for the wallpaper images
<@U02613K0X> thanks! can I use that tidy-federation as the base urls for the push endpoints?
yeah! i haven't had time to get any kind of docs going. i'll come talk to you <@U0261PCRQ>
<@U02688JHZ>: Hey sorry to get back to you so late! Jason and I have been combing through the styles. Jenny has set me up with the backend and I'll be working on getting some data flowing after this.
<@U0260V1BX|melissa> has left the channel
we got a note 4!
